726290f-a.title: Queens: Burns Street - 75th Road
726290f-a.text:
Burns Street, between 75th Road and Ascan Avenue, Forest
Hills, showing two-story homes on the north side of the street
and a 1ot--277 by 173 feet--on the south side. The view is north
from Beechknoll Road and shows, in the center background, a ten-
story building.called the Holland House. It is on the other side
of the Long Island Railroad tracks tn the depression and is on the
N.E. corner of Austin Street and 73rd Road.
Joseph P. Day  About 1930
Photographic Dept.
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE
